data.description: The home offers over 2600 square feet of living space, providing ample room for comfortable living. The kitchen has been beautifully upgraded with new counters, cupboards, flooring, & appliances. This is a significant improvement that can enhance both the functionality & aesthetics of the home. The living room features a wood-burning stove, which can create a cozy & inviting atmosphere during the colder months. It's not only practical but also adds character to the space. Newer carpets in the bedrooms & LVP flooring in the living room, kitchen, & mud/laundry room offer durability, ease of maintenance, & a modern look. Bathrooms on the main floor have been upgraded. Additionally, the bathroom upstairs features a new wrap-around shower. The upstairs bedroom has its own entrance & a walkout balcony, providing a private outdoor space to enjoy the views of the Majestic Spanish Peaks. The downstairs area is perfect for game nights, movies, and entertaining.
